_sText:
Simple wood and rope bridge prefab

Includes "triggers" for 2 seperate wood creaking "sounds" to be played when walking across. 
Also uses move_rope and keyframe_rope for rope type effect.

Game Type: HL2 - Source
Size: 124 width x 636 length
Textures: stock - Valve
Object Properties: function_detail
Sound Type: raw - "ambient/misc/wood1.wav" and "ambient/misc/wood2.wav"

Extract "ropewood_bridge.vmf"
To your "sourcesdk\bin\prefabs" directory

Free use of this prefab in any map without my permission, credit is not 
required.
